Package org.zone.region.flag.entity.player.interact.door

Class DoorInteractionFlag

java.lang.Object
org.zone.region.flag.entity.player.interact.door.DoorInteractionFlag
All Implemented Interfaces:
Flag, Flag.AffectsPlayer, Flag.GroupKeyed, Flag.TaggedFlag
public class DoorInteractionFlag extends Object implements Flag.TaggedFlag, Flag.AffectsPlayer
A flag to check if a player can open/close a door found within a region.

If the player is within a group that has the specified GroupKey then they can open/close blocks even with the flag enabled
